  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving maintenance practices for rural roads</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of this technical assistance is directed by the objectives defined in the overall WB project appraisal document which aims to (i) improve road access in rural areas and (ii) at the same time improve works implementation efficiency and the sustainability of rural road construction through improved maintenance. This ILO technical assistance focuses on the goal to develop more efficient maintenance arrangements for rural roads through improved policies, institutions, systems and implementation mechanisms.</narrative>
  </description>
